Method Detail

withDefaultNamedGraphUri

ModelBuilder.Builder withDefaultNamedGraphUri(Uri defaultUri)
Defines the URI of the default named graph of the to-be-built Model instance. The default named graph can later be queried by Model.defaultNamedGraph() method.

Triples that are added without specifying any named graph, are added to the default named graph.

Parameters:
defaultUri - the URI of the default named graph; must be non-null
Returns:
an object to handle the rest of the procedure of the model creation
